Utilities 2.0.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
io.github.utk003.util.data
A package for utility classes involved in manipulating and storing data.
io.github.utk003.util.data.collection
A package for custom collections not provided by Java.
io.github.utk003.util.data.collection.bijection
A package for the custom collection Bijection.
io.github.utk003.util.data.reference
A package for different types of references to objects.
io.github.utk003.util.data.tuple
A package for both mutable and immutable tuples.
io.github.utk003.util.data.tuple.immutable
A package for immutable tuples.
io.github.utk003.util.data.tuple.mutable
A package for mutable tuples.
io.github.utk003.util.func
A package that contains FunctionalInterfaces which represent value-returning and void lambda functions with varying numbers of parameters.
io.github.utk003.util.misc
A package for other miscellaneous utility classes.
io.github.utk003.util.perm
A package for permutation-related utility classes.
